{"tid":904053,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[熟車嘅入]最大馬力，最大扭力","createTime":"2018-11-16T04:37:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T09:27:44.000Z","uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1809c15b52a07834dab01a63a9aa819a67d0ed06","tid":904053,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T04:37:11.000Z","msg":"其實想問好耐<br />\n有時我見人去驗部車嘅馬力<br />\n好多時未扭到最高轉數已經到左最大馬力個位，之後條曲線會下降返<br />\n<br />\n例如說一個最高一萬轉嘅引擎<br />\n個馬力曲線去到8000轉已經係頂點，再扭到9000-10000轉時條曲線會下行<br />\n<br />\n問題來了，咁點解實際上扭到10000轉時會行得快過已經係頂點嘅8000轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n扭力都係一樣<br />\n<br />\n係唔係我理解錯左&ldquo;最大馬力&rdquo;依個詞？"},{"pid":"4976cb09726ba2682e37c9b11d18759d828bc81f","tid":904053,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":26,"score":-26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T04:55:17.000Z","msg":"馬力=power<br />\n扭力=torque<br />\ntorque=F&times;r<br />\nF=ma<br />\nv=u+at<br />\n咁都唔明我真係唔知點算好"},{"pid":"46ff0bfe2c7ddc18ed1204fcda38bfc641304a3c","tid":904053,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:19:02.000Z","msg":"再簡單<br />\n(棍波/DCT/)車輪轉速=引擎轉速&divide;波箱減速比&divide;尾牙減比<br />\n條式係冇扭力同馬力份，即係你只要上得到10000轉就係嗰個速度，同你中間用咩馬力同扭力去上到10000轉係無關係"},{"pid":"be6dc7cc1a68e5222b03a99d411e610e4a113cc1","tid":904053,"uid":138834,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4976cb09726ba2682e37c9b11d18759d828bc81f","tid":904053,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":26,"score":-26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T04:55:17.000Z","msg":"馬力=power<br />\n扭力=torque<br />\ntorque=F&times;r<br />\nF=ma<br />\nv=u+at<br />\n咁都唔明我真係唔知點算好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:20:19.000Z","msg":"用返v=u+at依條式<br />\nu係初速，a係加速度，t係時間，v係最終速度<br />\npower係唔係直接影響a<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n或者有圖會清楚啲<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.carstuff.com.tw/images/stories/EDISON/20100903/20100903pgo03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.carstuff.com.tw%2Fimages%2Fstories%2FEDISON%2F20100903%2F20100903pgo03.jpg&h=b1d0dbb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上圖架車個馬力去到8750轉已經係最大馬力，由圖睇9000轉時個馬力係細過8750轉時嘅馬力<br />\n<br />\n但實際上扭到九千幾時個速度反而會加少少<br />\n<br />\n唔明依到"},{"pid":"c4d089151d215ad7f1e43e3595390d1bbe5aff46","tid":904053,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46ff0bfe2c7ddc18ed1204fcda38bfc641304a3c","tid":904053,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:19:02.000Z","msg":"再簡單<br />\n(棍波/DCT/)車輪轉速=引擎轉速&divide;波箱減速比&divide;尾牙減比<br />\n條式係冇扭力同馬力份，即係你只要上得到10000轉就係嗰個速度，同你中間用咩馬力同扭力去上到10000轉係無關係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:28:17.000Z","msg":"好似明左少少<br />\n如果兩個引擎<br />\n兩邊都最高一萬轉，負載條件全部一樣<br />\n但一轉馬力大啲，一邊細啲<br />\n馬力差別係反映左係<br />\n兩邊由零轉拉到一萬轉嘅所需時間到？"},{"pid":"907779593d2958f8253b0b94a9f966e74a07bacc","tid":904053,"uid":4934,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:29:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/u-MH4sf5xkY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fu-MH4sf5xkY&d=sDlfSdw5COyVDtaB0INsCywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=6e1e5366\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/u-MH4sf5xkY</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mRROa_plpTc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmRROa_plpTc&d=sDlfSdw5COyVDtaB0INsCywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=9db6fafc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mRROa_plpTc</a>"},{"pid":"2c1868a0357dc52edaf9567823b10f5d20a4fdab","tid":904053,"uid":76216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"be6dc7cc1a68e5222b03a99d411e610e4a113cc1","tid":904053,"uid":138834,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4976cb09726ba2682e37c9b11d18759d828bc81f","tid":904053,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":26,"score":-26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T04:55:17.000Z","msg":"馬力=power<br />\n扭力=torque<br />\ntorque=F&times;r<br />\nF=ma<br />\nv=u+at<br />\n咁都唔明我真係唔知點算好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:20:19.000Z","msg":"用返v=u+at依