反而會加少少<br />\n<br />\n唔明依到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:32:16.000Z","msg":"我諗你應該係想問<br />\n<br />\n理應轉數同馬力係成正比 轉數高 馬力高  係線性黎<br />\n<br />\n但實際上 轉數同馬力係有 峰值 之後會下降 你曲線<br />\n<br />\n你想知個中因由下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:34:08.000Z","msg":"請指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04c7014daa08e0e5ae390d213b6b6d18e864fc74","tid":904053,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e46b8e431c254ee24e5956d07fe1442bed50551","tid":904053,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c1868a0357dc52edaf9567823b10f5d20a4fdab","tid":904053,"uid":76216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"be6dc7cc1a68e5222b03a99d411e610e4a113cc1","tid":904053,"uid":138834,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:20:19.000Z","msg":"用返v=u+at依條式<br />\nu係初速，a係加速度，t係時間，v係最終速度<br />\npower係唔係直接影響a<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n或者有圖會清楚啲<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.carstuff.com.tw/images/stories/EDISON/20100903/20100903pgo03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.carstuff.com.tw%2Fimages%2Fstories%2FEDISON%2F20100903%2F20100903pgo03.jpg&h=b1d0dbb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上圖架車個馬力去到8750轉已經係最大馬力，由圖睇9000轉時個馬力係細過8750轉時嘅馬力<br />\n<br />\n但實際上扭到九千幾時個速度反而會加少少<br />\n<br />\n唔明依到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:32:16.000Z","msg":"我諗你應該係想問<br />\n<br />\n理應轉數同馬力係成正比 轉數高 馬力高  係線性黎<br />\n<br />\n但實際上 轉數同馬力係有 峰值 之後會下降 你曲線<br />\n<br />\n你想知個中因由下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:34:08.000Z","msg":"請指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:35:27.000Z","msg":"我都唔識  我只係解釋你想法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39a709d2446cbb377f6a198f38bf6b044e765fc4","tid":904053,"uid":83469,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:01:10.000Z","msg":"因為車速未到最大馬力上限<br />\n我試過揸125cc逆風時上到7000轉（最大馬力）就冇得再上"},{"pid":"f1f25e7adcdad00ee234d6dd3b4f390b7cea6cfa","tid":904053,"uid":76216,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8e46b8e431c254ee24e5956d07fe1442bed50551","tid":904053,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c1868a0357dc52edaf9567823b10f5d20a4fdab","tid":904053,"uid":76216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"be6dc7cc1a68e5222b03a99d411e610e4a113cc1","tid":904053,"uid":138834,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:20:19.000Z","msg":"用返v=u+at依條式<br />\nu係初速，a係加速度，t係時間，v係最終速度<br />\npower係唔係直接影響a<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n或者有圖會清楚啲<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.carstuff.com.tw/images/stories/EDISON/20100903/20100903pgo03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.carstuff.com.tw%2Fimages%2Fstories%2FEDISON%2F20100903%2F20100903pgo03.jpg&h=b1d0dbb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上圖架車個馬力去到8750轉已經係最大馬力，由圖睇9000轉時個馬力係細過8750轉時嘅馬力<br />\n<br />\n但實際上扭到九千幾時個速度反而會加少少<br />\n<br />\n唔明依到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:32:16.000Z","msg":"我諗你應該係想問<br />\n<br />\n理應轉數同馬力係成正比 轉數高 馬力高  係線性黎<br />\n<br />\n但實際上 轉數同馬力係有 峰值 之後會下降 你曲線<br />\n<br />\n你想知個中因由下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:34:08.000Z","msg":"請指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:01:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.answers.yahoo.com/question/index?qid=20100928000015KK06529\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.answers.yahoo.com%2Fquestion%2Findex%3Fqid%3D20100928000015KK06529&d=sDlfSdw5COyVDtaB0INsCywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=aed5114a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.answers.yahoo.com/question/index?qid=20100928000015KK06529</a><br />\n超過最佳狀態馬力會下降是為&nbsp;<br />\n１．爆炸力會從活塞環漏氣&nbsp;<br />\n２．汽門無法應付幾乎連續之進排氣&nbsp;<br />\n３．排氣管內氣體過度膨脹無法順利排出&nbsp;<br />\n４．自然進氣無法強制給氣（因此有渦輪出現）&nbsp;<br />\n５．油膜量減少附著（賽車潤滑系統通常加大很多）&nbsp;<br />\n６．肉眼無法查覺高速機件及連桿擠壓變形&nbsp;<br />\n７．機件震動間隙&nbsp;<br />\n８．正時皮帶高速時會拉伸影響正時&nbsp;<br />\n９．有無可變汽門．正時提前．應付各轉速之變化&nbsp;<br />\n１０．空氣中含氧量無法再增加&nbsp;<br />\n１１．環保裝置限制馬力&nbsp;"},{"pid":"3a242fba401f8ddcd204640121102fea93322102","tid":904053,"uid":9526,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:20:38.000Z","msg":"速度係SLOPE黎....<br />\n<br />\n你POWER同SPEED都唔係成正比<br />\n你FOCUS左係POWER個上升同下降<br />\n<br />\n例如佢7000轉最大馬力 300 過左之後10000轉會跌到280<br />\n只係加速度減低左, SPEED仍然係10000轉 最快<br />\n<br />\n你最戈句 咩實際上到10000轉會行得快過8000轉 係講緊SPEED<br />\n而你前面研究緊係POWER下降...."},{"pid":"07f61c06591cc7ef47d384567db3b8b19574a7a5","tid":904053,"uid":10845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:32:16.000Z","msg":"留名學野。<br />\n0-100如果要快扭力重要定馬力？"},{"pid":"8b44ebddcbb2c2968f41441ffef579ef32521ba9","tid":904053,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"07f61c06591cc7ef47d384567db3b8b19574a7a5","tid":904053,"uid":10845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:32:16.000Z","msg":"留名學野。<br />\n0-100如果要快扭力重要定馬力？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:41:02.000Z","msg":"馬力<br />\n因為 馬力 = 扭力 x 轉速<br />\n馬力大就扭力同轉速一齊大 <br />\n好似係"},{"pid":"187be5cba6ad6135e78aada20f422c0c61fc31cc","tid":904053,"uid":10845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b44ebddcbb2c2968f41441ffef579ef32521ba9","tid":904053,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"07f61c06591cc7ef47d384567db3b8b19574a7a5","tid":904053,"uid":10845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:32:16.000Z","msg":"留名學野。<br />\n0-100如果要快扭力重要定馬力？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:41:02.000Z","msg":"馬力<br />\n因為 馬力 = 扭力 x 轉速<br />\n馬力大就扭力同轉速一齊大 <br />\n好似係"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:44:00.000Z","msg":"學到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我有樣野想問<br />\n二架重量引擎一樣既車<br />\n250hp 320扭力 <br />\n220hp 380扭力<br />\n邊部0-100會快d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真心想知。"},{"pid":"fac02e706f122fc579aece7a8022627a7f556c97","tid":904053,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"187be5cba6ad6135e78aada20f422c0c61fc31cc","tid":904053,"uid":10845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b44ebddcbb2c2968f41441ffef579ef32521ba9","tid":904053,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"07f61c06591cc7ef47d384567db3b8b19574a7a5","tid":904053,"uid":10845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:32:16.000Z","msg":"留名學野。<br />\n0-100如果要快扭力重要定馬力？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:41:02.000Z","msg":"馬力<br />\n因為 馬力 = 扭力 x 轉速<br />\n馬力大就扭力同轉速一齊大 <br />\n好似係"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:44:00.000Z","msg":"學到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我有樣野想問<br />\n二架重量引擎一樣既車<br />\n250hp 320扭力 <br />\n220hp 380扭力<br />\n邊部0-100會快d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真心想知。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T07:03:39.000Z","msg":"個數字係指最大數值，要睇埋轉速<br />\n馬=扭&times;轉&times;constant<br />\n01快唔快仲要睇埋波箱、尾牙、車重<br />\n不過咁<br />\n如果有380Nm扭力而得220匹馬力，即係副偈低中速扭飽滿但高轉扭力跌得快或者上唔到好高轉，<br />\n相反320Nm扭力而有250匹馬就代表高轉仍然有一定扭力輸出，轉速亦相對較高"},{"pid":"64dc7a38146e7a1cc5bc3988675a25390f660a57","tid":904053,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"187be5cba6ad6135e78aada20f422c0c61fc31cc","tid":904053,"uid":10845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b44ebddcbb2c2968f41441ffef579ef32521ba9","tid":904053,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"07f61c06591cc7ef47d384567db3b8b19574a7a5","tid":904053,"uid":10845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:32:16.000Z","msg":"留名學野。<br />\n0-100如果要快扭力重要定馬力？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:41:02.000Z","msg":"馬力<br />\n因為 馬力 = 扭力 x 轉速<br />\n馬力大就扭力同轉速一齊大 <br />\n好似係"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:44:00.000Z","msg":"學到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我有樣野想問<br />\n二架重量引擎一樣既車<br />\n250hp 320扭力 <br />\n220hp 380扭力<br />\n邊部0-100會快d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真心想知。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T07:08:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.cdn.circlesix.co/image/1/400/0/uploads/posts/2016/02/5e6bdb2d85d78236e890210bb81fe29b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.cdn.circlesix.co%2Fimage%2F1%2F400%2F0%2Fuploads%2Fposts%2F2016%2F02%2F5e6bdb2d85d78236e890210bb81fe29b.jpg&h=ef5cf997&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你可以試下plug啲數入去試下 可以揾到邊個rpm高啲 但係唔代表會0-100會快啲 <br />\n<br />\n0-100比較複雜 因為部車既扭力唔會係一個constant eg. 320Nm@5000rpm 之類 係唔同rpm都有唔同扭力 呢個又關係到gear ratio 所以有啲複雜 <br />\n其實我都唔係好識 等高手解答啦"},{"pid":"2f5ec619be70be597f1af9eb197863c04fa944f6","tid":904053,"uid":148636,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T07:49:19.000Z","msg":"其實你想像下自己踩單車就得<br />\n你個人就係個引擎<br />\n要你一分鐘踩30下, 60下, 90下, 同120下, 你個輸出都唔同<br />\n馬力係扭力x轉數x constant<br />\n最大馬力只不過係講緊呢一條數乘出黎最大個一個位<br />\n同加速力既關係大過速度<br />\n假設你本身個人扭力最好係60-90個一段<br />\n係代表你可以好快由60轉踩到上90轉<br />\n再上你可能會開始吃力, 但係你上到120轉係齒輪比一樣既情況下一定快過90轉"},{"pid":"53d0e7a2173253f02de205ace3a0d9a28c7828c8","tid":904053,"uid":162259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T08:03:17.000Z","msg":"9000 轉「快」過 7000 = speed快啲<br />\n7000 轉「快」過 9000 = acceleration大啲 （馬力大啲）"},{"pid":"d28db9e3e46531299d76306a4e5554b6445ae751","tid":904053,"uid":12447,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T08:20:12.000Z","msg":"馬力係極速<br />\n扭力係加速<br />\n啲車0-100好快 係扭力上限<br />\n200係極 100打後就慢慢先上到"},{"pid":"547c0d35fdf7ece244069bbb320381845e2ae40a","tid":904053,"uid":12447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d28db9e3e46531299d76306a4e5554b6445ae751","tid":904053,"uid":12447,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T08:20:12.000Z","msg":"馬力係極速<br />\n扭力係加速<br />\n啲車0-100好快 係扭力上限<br />\n200係極 100打後就慢慢先上到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T08:21:24.000Z","msg":"有啲車改到極速好低從而加強個加速度<br />\nPS: NFS8 學返來"},{"pid":"a6f3c98a514a9321293eae70e45adbd9de712540","tid":904053,"uid":12447,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T08:22:50.000Z","msg":"直路玩馬力<br />\n山路玩扭力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9219b3d41630ceb3f84391b9019bf6428c5aa20","tid":904053,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T08:32:17.000Z","msg":"好彩係開係車台，真心學到野<br />\n<br />\n係學術台一定一堆傻仔衝入嚟"},{"pid":"77f7c41711d8ebb9272a9723bcbe964b293e9659","tid":904053,"uid":10845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6f3c98a514a9321293eae70e45adbd9de712540","tid":904053,"uid":12447,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T08:22:50.000Z","msg":"直路玩馬力<br />\n山路玩扭力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T13:19:27.000Z","msg":"意思係中段60kmh-120kmh範圍內扭力重要過馬力？<br />\n真心唔識。有錯唔好屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54d92c30fa6b6845b54685bb388e8de5a215cdb1","tid":904053,"uid":6636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77f7c41711d8ebb9272a9723bcbe964b293e9659","tid":904053,"uid":10845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6f3c98a514a9321293eae70e45adbd9de712540","tid":904053,"uid":12447,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T08:22:50.000Z","msg":"直路玩馬力<br />\n山路玩扭力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T13:19:27.000Z","msg":"意思係中段60kmh-120kmh範圍內扭力重要過馬力？<br />\n真心唔識。有錯唔好屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T22:24:01.000Z","msg":"山路多灣 出灣要快就要大扭力<br />\n好似係"}]}